Name: The Dreaming Fox
About the game: The Dreaming Fox is a simple, clicker game that is meant for you to pass time while enjoying a soothing soundtrack and simple scenery. You will play as the dreaming fox and have to avoid obstacles. See how far you can take your fox dream. • Soundtrack composed by Solos • Illustrated by Spica Illustrations
